examples.example_description:
`DatePicker.SingleMonth` is simple select to choose the month in a year.
```jsx live
function SingleMonthExample() {
  const [value, setValue] = React.useState();
  return (
    <DatePicker.SingleMonth
      value={value}
      onChange={setValue}
      id="single-month-picker"
      placeholder="Single Month"
      minMonth={3}
      maxMonth={9}
    />
  );
}
```

